TITLE: Initializing and Handling Navigation with Dynamic Configuration in React Navigation
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates how to initialize and handle navigation using a dynamic configuration in React Navigation. It includes the creation of a navigation container ref, a custom navigate function for checking navigation readiness, and the setup of a dynamic navigation structure.
SOURCE: https://github.com/react-navigation/react-navigation.github.io/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-7.x/navigating-without-navigation-prop.md#2025-04-23_snippet_7

