DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates customizing shared element transitions by defining a custom transition function with react-native-reanimated's SharedTransition.custom. It uses withSpring for animating size and position properties and sets the resulting sharedTransitionStyle prop on Animated.Image components. Dependencies include react-native-reanimated and its SharedTransition and withSpring exports. Key parameters are values object (target dimensions/origins) provided to the transition worklet, and sharedTransitionStyle applied to each element. Inputs are element property changes and outputs are smooth spring-based transitions; customizing transform requires additional logic not shown here.
