TITLE: Adding Tab Bar Icons with Dynamic Configuration in React Native
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to add icons to a bottom tab bar using the dynamic (component-based) configuration with `createBottomTabNavigator`. It uses the `Tab.Navigator` component and its `screenOptions` prop to define a `tabBarIcon` function, which conditionally renders an `Ionicons` component. Dependencies include `@react-navigation/native`, `@react-navigation/bottom-tabs`, `@expo/vector-icons` (or `react-native-vector-icons`), and `react`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/react-navigation/react-navigation.github.io/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-7.x/customizing-bottom-tabs.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: js
