SOURCE: https://github.com/react-navigation/react-navigation.github.io/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-6.x/configuring-links.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { NavigationContainer } from '@react-navigation/native';

const linking = {
  prefixes: [
    /* your linking prefixes */
  ],
  config: {
    /* configuration for matching screens with paths */
  },
};

function App() {
  return (
    <NavigationContainer linking={linking} fallback={<Text>Loading...</Text>}>
      {/* content */}
    </NavigationContainer>
  );
}
```

