TITLE: iOS Deep Linking Configuration in AppDelegate.m (iOS 9+)
DESCRIPTION: This Objective-C code shows how to modify the AppDelegate.m file to handle deep links in iOS 9 and newer. It implements the application:openURL:options: method to handle incoming URLs using RCTLinkingManager.
