CODE:
```
const opacity = Animated.add(progress.current, progress.next || 0).interpolate({
  inputRange: [0, 1, 2],
  outputRange: [0, 1, 0],
});

return (
  <Animated.View style={{ opacity }}>{/* Header content */}</Animated.View>
);
```

