SOURCE: https://github.com/react-navigation/react-navigation.github.io/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-5.x/configuring-links.md#_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const config = {
  screens: {
    Profile: {
      path: 'user/:id/:section?',
      parse: {
        id: (id) => `user-${id}`,
      },
      stringify: {
        id: (id) => id.replace(/^user-/, ''),
      },
    },
  },
};
```

