TITLE: Customizing Tab Navigation with Icons in React Native
DESCRIPTION: Example of customizing the appearance of tab navigation by adding icons and custom colors. Uses the screenOptions prop to define icons based on the route and focused state, and tabBarOptions to customize colors.
SOURCE: https://github.com/react-navigation/react-navigation.github.io/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-5.x/tab-based-navigation.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: js
