TITLE: Cross-Fading Headers Using Animated Opacity - React Navigation (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates animating the header's opacity during header transitions in React Navigation by interpolating progress.current and progress.next using Animated.add and interpolate. Useful when using headerMode: 'float' for floating custom headers. Assumes use of React Native's Animated API and is generally intended for advanced header animations.
