TITLE: Creating Custom Navigation Helper in React Navigation
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a custom navigation helper function 'insertBeforeLast' that inserts a new screen just before the last one in the navigation stack.
SOURCE: https://github.com/react-navigation/react-navigation.github.io/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-7.x/navigation-object.md#2025-04-23_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { CommonActions } from '@react-navigation/native';

const insertBeforeLast = (routeName, params) => (state) => {
  const routes = [
    ...state.routes.slice(0, -1),
    { name: routeName, params },
    state.routes[state.routes.length - 1],
  ];

  return CommonActions.reset({
    ...state,
    routes,
    index: routes.length - 1,
  });
};
```

