TITLE: Controlling Drawer Navigation in React Navigation
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to programmatically control the drawer navigation using navigation props and DrawerActions. It includes methods to open, close, and toggle the drawer, as well as how to check if the drawer is open.
