TITLE: Defining Static Screen Component at Top Level for React Navigation (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet correctly defines the 'Home' screen at the top level before using it in the Stack.Navigator. This preserves component identity, prevents unwanted remounts, and ensures persistent navigation and local state. No additional dependencies are required besides React and React Navigation.
