TITLE: Dispatching Navigation Actions via App Container Ref (JavaScript/React)
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to obtain a reference to the `AppContainer` instance using the `ref` prop in a React class component. This ref (`this.navigator`) can then be used to call the `dispatch` method on the navigator, allowing navigation actions (e.g., using `NavigationActions.navigate`) to be triggered programmatically from outside the navigation screens, such as in response to component events like `someEvent`.
