SOURCE: https://github.com/react-navigation/react-navigation.github.io/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-3.x/navigation-options-resolution.md#2025-04-23_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
const FeedStack = createStackNavigator({
  FeedHome: FeedScreen,
  Details: DetailsScreen,
});

