TITLE: Applying Themes to navigationOptions using screenProps
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to apply themes to navigationOptions in a stack navigator. Since navigationOptions can't directly access React context, this snippet demonstrates using screenProps as a workaround to apply theme styles to the header.
