TITLE: Header Style Fade Animation Interpolator
DESCRIPTION: Custom header style interpolator function that creates fade effects for header elements.
SOURCE: https://github.com/react-navigation/react-navigation.github.io/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-4.x/stack-navigator.md#2025-04-23_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const forFade = ({ current, next }) => {
  const opacity = Animated.add(
    current.progress,
    next ? next.progress : 0
  ).interpolate({
    inputRange: [0, 1, 2],
    outputRange: [0, 1, 0],
  });

  return {
    leftButtonStyle: { opacity },
    rightButtonStyle: { opacity },
    titleStyle: { opacity },
    backgroundStyle: { opacity },
  };
};
```

